title: 249. Summer Series Takeover 2021 #1: RWR McDonald and Dinuka McKenzie
itunes:author: Words and Nerds: Authors, books and literature.
itunes:summary: This episode is part of the Summer Series Takeover 2021 where a friend of the pod, a writer or illustrator who has been interviewed on the podcast, chooses an author of their choice to chat about books, writing, going home for the holidays, becoming an artist and any other topic they choose. Enjoy!
